  "detailed_description": "<i>\"A birdie flew across the roof yesterday.<br>She said she’ll fly over again today.\"</i><br><br>From a decade ago, by the creator of <i><strong>To the Moon</strong></i> and <i><strong>Finding Paradise</strong></i>: A 30-minute experimental adventure game about a faceless girl stuck inside a house with no door to the outside. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A short play fitting for a single sitting.<br></li><li>A lousy original soundtrack consisting of one single tune.<br></li><li>An abstract experience that you hereby agree not to sue the developer for.</li></ul>",
